Package org.drip.state.identifier

Class OvernightLabel

java.lang.Object
org.drip.state.identifier.FloaterLabel
org.drip.state.identifier.ForwardLabel
org.drip.state.identifier.OvernightLabel
All Implemented Interfaces:
LatentStateLabel
public class OvernightLabel
extends ForwardLabel
OvernightLabel contains the Index Parameters referencing an Overnight Index. It provides the functionality to Retrieve Index, Tenor, Currency, and Fully Qualified Name.

  • Module = Product Core Module
  • Library = Fixed Income Analytics
  • Project = Latent State Inference and Creation Utilities
  • Package = Latent State Identifier Labels

Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
